there's so much hope that goes along
with ending a relationship

931
01:03:58.505 --> 01:04:00.382
and starting a new chapter.

932
01:04:08.223 --> 01:04:09.891
Some of my favorite lyrics are
in that song.

933
01:04:09.974 --> 01:04:13.061
I really like the. "I hope he took
his bad deal and made a royal flush."

934
01:04:13.144 --> 01:04:15.522
I was writing that song in my bedroom
or living room or something.

935
01:04:15.605 --> 01:04:18.149
I remember going into the other room
where my dad was. and I was like.

936
01:04:18.233 --> 01:04:21.069
"Hey. Dad. What's the best card hand
that you can have?"

937
01:04:21.152 --> 01:04:23.697
He goes. "Royal flush." I'm like.
"Perfect. That rhymes with something."

938
01:04:23.780 --> 01:04:26.241
I go back in and. like.
put it in the song.

939
