01:04:34.666 --> 01:04:35.959
-I have lots of thoughts.
-Okay.

942
01:04:36.459 --> 01:04:39.629
[Nigro] But let's make some.
let's make some steps.

943
01:04:39.713 --> 01:04:43.258
I just-- I just want. um. "brutal"
to be the first track.

944
01:04:43.341 --> 01:04:45.301
-You really do?
-I really do.

945
01:04:46.636 --> 01:04:48.930
