my work cut out for me this weekend.

946
01:04:49.014 --> 01:04:50.015
I know.

947
01:04:50.098 --> 01:04:51.516
[Nigro coughs]

948
01:04:51.599 --> 01:04:55.020
Wait. Sorry. I wasn't ready.
I wasn't ready. I wasn't ready.

949
01:04:55.103 --> 01:04:56.104
Okay. I'm ready.

