01:05:52.285 --> 01:05:53.328
Should I print it?

966
01:05:53.411 --> 01:05:54.996
-Yeah.
-Yeah. You feel good about it?

967
01:05:55.080 --> 01:05:56.915
I'm gonna cry!

968
01:05:56.998 --> 01:05:58.291
[Nigro laughs]

969
01:05:59.042 --> 01:06:01.795
-I'm gonna cry.
