spent in this studio.

972
01:06:10.428 --> 01:06:13.473
[Nigro] I know.
Nothing will ever be the same.

973
01:06:13.973 --> 01:06:16.101
No. Hopefully not.

974
01:06:16.184 --> 01:06:19.062
Hopefully it won't be so sad
in the next **** record.

975
01:06:19.145 --> 01:06:22.857
[Nigro chuckling] It's like--
it's a bittersweet feeling.

976
01:06:22.941 --> 01:06:25.110
[Rodrigo chuckles] I know. So bittersweet.

977
01:06:25.193 --> 01:06:28.363
It's definitely. like.
the-last-day-of-school feeling.

978
01:06:35.245 --> 01:06:38.873
Coming from this place of hurt
and devastation.

979
01:06:38.957 --> 01:06:42.711
and you manage to turn it into something
that you're proud of

980
01:06:42.794 --> 01:06:44.629
and something that other people can enjoy.

981
01:06:44.713 --> 01:06:51.678
and something that brings acceptance
and. like. light and joy into the world.

982
01:06:51.761 --> 01:06:53.471
there's. like. nothing better than that.

983
01:06:53.555 --> 01:06:55.807
And there's. like. not a day
that. like. goes by

984
01:06:55.890 --> 01:06:58.143
that I'm not grateful for that opportunity

985
01:06:58.226 --> 01:07:01.563
and so proud of myself
that I. like. did that too.

986
01:07:07.402 --> 01:07:10.947
I've grown. like. five years' worth…
[chuckles] …in. like. one year.

987
01:07:11.031 --> 01:07:14.367
I think I'm so much of a different person
in a good way.

988
01:07:14.451 --> 01:07:18.621
I think I had to learn how to have. like.
thick skin and how to stand up for myself.

989
01:07:18.705 --> 01:07:21.499
And I think I just wanted to tell people
what was going on

990
01:07:21.583 --> 01:07:25.045
in the depths of my heart
and in the back of my head

991
01:07:25.128 --> 01:07:27.464
in a way that was proud.

992
01:07:30.633 --> 01:07:34.763
I think there's something so powerful
about that. especially as a young woman.

